{"tid":534460,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人覺得一本本既實體漫畫，好睇過電子版好多","createTime":"2018-01-19T20:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T03:00:52.000Z","uid":56911,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7bdf365d835d76810727921b6f40a4693ad74d0e","tid":534460,"uid":56911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T20:30:38.000Z","msg":"利申平時無睇開動漫台<br />\n<br />\n我本身好鍾意睇漫畫，但以前屋企無咩位放漫畫，係租漫畫為主<br />\n<br />\n而家大個喇想追返好幾套漫畫<br />\n買漫畫既錢唔係問題，但地方係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如想追返火影one piece 火鳳燎原 第一神拳<br />\n<br />\n已經百幾本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想知大家點儲存同收藏<br />\n電子版一來睇得無咁舒服，二來我想支持作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家仲要好似無哂合法租漫畫 / 漫畫cafe(如果有介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"ee97b9d5e27b1f9c567bc6c9fa464b9dbc155ee2","tid":534460,"uid":56911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T20:32:58.000Z","msg":"同埋我唔明用手機睇漫畫（有時仲要睇港漫）<br />\n唔會覺得好唔舒服架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d724e8162ad2daa94ebe727ba68df421bf63338","tid":534460,"uid":8307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T21:22:07.000Z","msg":"電子版都有正版可能支持既,amazon都有出個電子閱讀器,個畫面應該冇咁傷眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/705/22332483952_6149cef13f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.staticflickr.com%2F1%2F705%2F22332483952_6149cef13f.jpg&h=4fb8ecae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你講個啲漫畫都仲連載緊同好熱門,應該唔難搵返之前個啲<br />\n點樣保養,見人會幫漫畫包書皮,放落有門既櫃加幾粒防潮珠就ok<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手機睇漫畫個mon太細個,拎實體書睇對手又好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc3aa6af62765579119f812ac125ec6e5bc4daa","tid":534460,"uid":123969,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0d724e8162ad2daa94ebe727b