 />\n利申：復古撚，一年中會揀個日子燻書同書櫃上diy驅蟲油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:16:37.000Z","msg":"我就係覺得手感好好多﹐我好鍾意印刷品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實香港儲書應該好煩，好多濕既日子<br />\n<br />\n屋又細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2aa3f2e828079da0d9c388e8bd72370de71ef1b","tid":534460,"uid":56911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f53534cee28d451efbe52fdea9632c423c1f3c","tid":534460,"uid":90697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"香港實體漫畫難做<br />\n你買本書可能只是幾十元<br />\n但儲放空間可能是幾百元<br />\n再買多幾本可能無位放<br />\n香港地少人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:20:09.000Z","msg":"細個都儲過一段時間黑社會漫畫，到廿頭個時大執屋發現比人丟左<br />\n<br />\ncoco 成百本拎左去賣<br />\n<br />\n根本無位放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f374b7996569591cde06ab90034ac34cf9e29b2","tid":534460,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"我屋企都有千本漫畫左右<br />\n由細細個開始買<br />\n<br />\n而家出左國做野, 好掛住我屋企d書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第時買到樓要有一間做書房<br />\n<br />\n而家係日本同香港漫畫鋪訂書<br />\n屋胸一人過黎就一喼咁拖黎比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d12ab844ecc9476c9b4069dd615f3f1a886cf93","tid":534460,"uid":152097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"從享受角度，睇實體書爽好多。<br />\n<br />\n電子版冇心機去重睇，實體書得閒會攞上手刨下。<br />\n<br />\n屋企有位放書，可以俾我儲落去，但我儲緊既漫畫，好多套香港出版社已經放棄買版權，變相港版爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇見果幾套爛尾書就燥底。<br />\n<br />\n我反而想知，點解台灣可以咁勁，乜鳩書都代理返去出中文版，真係咁大市場?"},{"pid":"ba857cbc3080221c1124795f82ef0d5efbcc1bad","tid":534460,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"但冇位放嘛!<br />\n以前D龍珠/亂馬掉晒,得套GS美神仲留住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd590d98385b5a9bf53ad3af89ee6235b610227","tid":534460,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"買部ipad睇漫畫人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d334126f38fbcd6934ccde9631f0a394b9c90d40","tid":534460,"uid":90697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2aa3f2e828079da0d9c388e8bd72370de71ef1b","tid":534460,"uid":56911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f53534cee28d451efbe52fdea9632c423c1f3c","tid":534460,"uid":90697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"香港實體漫畫難做<br />\n你買本書可能只是幾十元<br />\n但儲放空間可能是幾百元<br />\n再買多幾本可能無位放<br />\n香港地少人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T03:20:09.000Z","msg":"細個都儲過一段時間黑社會漫畫，到廿頭個時大執屋發現比人丟左<br />\n<br />\ncoco 成百本拎左去賣<br />\n<br />\n根本無位放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"我細個都有儲。。。無奈越買越多仲屋企人都同我傾過。。。最後ko曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}